1
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 2=
(The Rebel Daughter-in-Law Arrives)

3
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:33,959
Good morning,

4
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,319
Qingmei.

5
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:38,680
Are you

6
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,079
He Jinchuan, my younger brother-in-law?

7
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:42,680
(He Jinchuan, Second Son)
You chose a good time

8
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,280
to lose your memory.

9
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:07,640
Look at the time now!

10
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,240
The guests will be arriving soon.

11
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,680
Now get to the kitchen and help out.

12
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:12,840
Mom,

13
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,840
Qingmei is now the heir
of Gu Corporation.

14
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,599
There's no way she could do housework.

15
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,599
The heir?

16
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:19,000
Once married into He family,

17
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,800
she must abide by the rules.

18
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,159
So a daughter-in-law in this family

19
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:25,120
is treated like a maid?

20
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,199
Jinxi,

21
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,039
when you get married,

22
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,879
you must keep your eyes wide open.

23
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,680
Mom.

24
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,759
Qingmei,

25
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,159
mom has high blood pressure.
Don't provoke her.

26
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,039
Fine, fine.

27
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,439
I'm on my way.

28
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:40,039
I'll step aside and leave you the stage.

29
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,039
Gu Qingmei.

30
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,280
Ever since she inherited
the family fortune,

31
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:48,280
she has become more and more arrogant.

32
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:50,080
Mom,

33
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,479
no rush.

34
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,280
she'll get what's coming to her soon.

35
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,240
Madam Gu,

36
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,280
you finally came to grace
the kitchen with your presence.

37
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,000
Perhaps you could wash some dishes.

38
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:00,879
I am afraid

39
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,120
chopping vegetables might
injure your precious hands.

40
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:06,400
Alright.

41
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:17,439
After the car accident, my hands

42
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:19,120
have been trembling badly.

43
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:21,000
This is Madam He's favorite plate!

44
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,080
Can you even afford it?

45
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,199
Me?

46
00:03:23,639 --> 00:03:24,639
Isn't this part of your job?

47
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:25,919
What does it have to do with me?

48
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,680
Ridiculous.

49
00:03:28,759 --> 00:03:30,639
But there is one thing
I don't understand.

50
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,919
Tell me,

51
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:33,719
there are two daughters-in-law,

52
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,439
why am I the only one
being used like a servant?

53
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,240
Today is Jinxi's day to shine.

54
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:48,039
Why are you all dressed up?

55
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,479
Who said it was for her?

56
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:52,599
Don't forget

57
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,879
Qingmei is still at home.

58
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,680
How can Qingmei compare to you?

59
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,439
In my heart,

60
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:57,800
you are the best, my dear.

61
00:03:58,759 --> 00:04:01,080
She is the heir of Gu Corporation now.

62
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,360
She might even try to
turn the tables later

63
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,520
and trample me underfoot.

64
00:04:04,599 --> 00:04:05,680
How could that be?

65
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:08,479
Mom, if anyone's mean to you,

66
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,759
I'll beat them up!

67
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,240
My son is the best.

68
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,080
Give Mommy a kiss.

69
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:13,759
Come here.

70
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,600
Good boy.

71
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,199
Shaoze.

72
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,959
You

73
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,839
remind me of your father.

74
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,079
I remember back then

75
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:27,319
(He Mingyuan, Chairman of Shengda Group)
when we started our business

76
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,480
(He Mingyuan, Chairman of Shengda Group)
and founded Shengda,

77
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,120
just like you now,

78
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,199
we were young and full of ambition.

79
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:35,079
If my father were here today,

80
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,759
seeing what Shengda has become,

81
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,240
he would be very pleased.

82
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,000
Age is catching up with me.

83
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,560
The future of Shengda

84
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,680
should be handed over
to the younger generation.

85
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,920
The VP position at Shengda

86
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,160
has been vacant for a while.

87
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,399
Now that you are back,

88
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,279
it is the perfect time for you
to gain experience at the company.

89
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,439
Uncle,

90
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:03,120
Shengda is in good hands
with you and Jinchen.

91
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,160
Since returning this time,

92
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:08,439
I have found that things back home are
much more interesting than before.

93
00:05:11,439 --> 00:05:14,319
I hear you're quite the investor abroad,

94
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:17,360
you had quite a life too.

95
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:19,160
Life...

96
00:05:20,079 --> 00:05:21,399
We only live once.

97
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,079
My father was such a workaholic.

98
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,040
He never got to enjoy life

99
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,240
before he passed away.

100
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,120
It was truly not worth it.

101
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,720
Jinxi

102
00:05:38,879 --> 00:05:39,959
is always asking

103
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,120
when you're coming back.

104
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,480
You were engaged as children.

105
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:46,040
Now that you are back.

106
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:46,759
Is it time

107
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,879
to set a date for the wedding?

108
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,120
Uncle He,

109
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:52,480
that was just a childhood joke.

110
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,959
Jinxi wouldn't take it seriously.

111
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,600
I know you young people.

112
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,120
Just spend more time together.

113
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,279
And feelings will naturally develop.

114
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:04,560
In any case, I have already
decided on you as my son-in-law.

115
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,600
Tonight,

116
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:08,720
let's sit down and have a drink.

117
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,600
You can stay at our house.

118
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,240
Haven't you wrapped it up yet?

119
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,639
Dinner is about to be served.

120
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:23,800
Oh, I am sorry.

121
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,279
You are so careless.

122
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:28,160
Dad,

123
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,279
The doctor said no cigars.

124
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,360
Wel...

125
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,079
You little bossy girl.

126
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,959
I should have married you off long ago.

127
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,600
Come on, Dad.

128
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:53,360
Is Qingmei not joining us for dinner?

129
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,240
She's lending a hand in the kitchen.

130
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,600
So ill-mannered.

131
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,120
Get back to the kitchen.

132
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:13,680
Mom,

133
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,759
your rules are interesting,

134
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:19,160
making the eldest daughter-in-law
do all the serving.

135
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,519
Is this the He family's
way of treating guests?

136
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:22,959
How unique.

137
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:23,839
You...

138
00:07:23,839 --> 00:07:24,439
My apology, Qingmei.

139
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:27,680
I'm honored

140
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,959
that you cook yourself just for me.

141
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,279
Let us all dine together.

142
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:33,720
Otherwise, I would feel uneasy.

143
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,920
(Why is this man speaking up for me?)

144
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:37,600
(Do I know him?)

145
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,040
Exactly.

146
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:43,600
Today is Qingmei's first family
dinner since she was discharged,

147
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:47,079
and it also serves as
a welcome dinner for Shaoze.

148
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,160
We are family.

149
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,839
Please dive in.

150
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:51,800
Come.

151
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,480
Cheers.

152
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,439
Shaoze.

153
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:09,079
Thank you for taking Qingmei
to the hospital that day.

154
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,519
We are family. It was my duty.

155
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,879
You saved me that day?

156
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,600
Then do you know...

157
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:16,519
What bad luck.

158
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,800
With this injury,

159
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:20,000
there's no telling
if you can still conceive.

160
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,240
Look at Niannian.

161
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,439
She married here the same year as you.

162
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,759
And An'an is already five years old.

163
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,360
Wait.

164
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,559
Married for four years.

165
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,879
Your son is five years old.

166
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,399
You have been quite fast.

167
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,519
May I ask

168
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,960
if you got married because of pregnancy?

169
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,360
How long did you date
before getting married?

170
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,120
Have you ever considered

171
00:08:42,279 --> 00:08:43,519
whether such a marriage can really last?

172
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:44,639
Well...

173
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,080
Of course I haven't.

174
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,320
Then was it a business marriage?

175
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:49,120
Can a marriage bound by such interests

176
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,120
bring happiness?

177
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,639
Qingmei,

178
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:02,120
you are just like a journalist.

179
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,159
A journalist?

180
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,399
Am I?

181
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,679
I am just a little curious.

182
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,279
Ever since your head injury,

183
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,519
you've started thinking
in such a strange way.

184
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:14,279
Sorry.

185
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:15,639
I forgot.

186
00:09:15,879 --> 00:09:17,200
The secrets of wealthy families

187
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,679
are not meant to be spoken aloud.

188
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,360
(Gu Qingmei,)

189
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,559
(you just keep getting
more interesting.)

190
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:37,120
Leave this file with me for now.

191
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:38,559
Su Li has been out of contact for days.

192
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:39,559
I am worried something happened to her.

193
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:41,200
Don't worry.

194
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,879
She is like a cat

195
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,639
with nine lives.

196
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,000
That is true.

197
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:49,480
A person who dared to storm a drug den
in Southeast Asia alone.

198
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,480
Most men probably cannot even beat her.

199
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:56,960
An'an.

200
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:00,720
So picky about food.

201
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,759
No wonder you're still so short.

202
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,120
You are not picky. So what?

203
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,679
Spray me again if you dare.

204
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:14,559
Try it one more time.

205
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,480
Will you spray?

206
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,480
Spray.

207
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,240
Little brat.

208
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:40,960
Madam Gu,

209
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,559
we have a guest from the auction.

210
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,360
For me?

211
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,000
(Auction Payment Receipt)
Mrs. He,

212
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,200
(Auction Payment Receipt)
for the two pieces of jewelry you bid,

213
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,000
(Auction Payment Receipt)
plus service fees,

214
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:53,759
(Auction Confirmation Certificate)
it's 18,880,000 in total.

215
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,600
Here is the breakdown.

216
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,240
18,880,000?

217
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,759
That is quite an auspicious number.

218
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,240
You have the right person?

219
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:06,080
Yes, you are the one who won the bid.

220
00:11:06,279 --> 00:11:08,080
And you took them on the spot.

221
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,120
There is even your signature here.

222
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:12,780
(Buyer: Gu Qingmei)

223
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:14,840
Impossible.

224
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,000
I have never seen
that much money in my entire life.

225
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,519
You're faking amnesia again.

226
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,960
Everyone in the hall saw you
outbid everyone else.

227
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,360
Until now, I haven't seen

228
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,679
what those two pieces look like.

229
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,080
And when I woke up, they were not on me.

230
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,320
How can you expect me to pay for that?

231
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,039
That is your own fault for losing them.

232
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:30,799
Pay the bill now.

233
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,080
Don't embarrass yourself here.

234
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:48,320
It is partly my fault too.

235
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,519
I was so focused on
saving lives at the time

236
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,120
that I did not notice whether Qingmei

237
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:53,399
carried any valuables.

238
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,159
Maybe I lost them somehow.

239
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,879
Shaoze,

240
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:58,720
you saved her life.

241
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,919
What does this have to do with you?

242
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:02,000
They are collecting the debt now,

243
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,120
it won't reflect well if this gets out.

244
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:05,759
It is not that much money anyway.

245
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:08,279
I'll pay for it.

246
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,200
No need, Shaoze.

247
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,399
I will cover it.

248
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:16,840
Well...

249
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:28,159
So this is the wealthy life
I used to have.

250
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:29,559
Not that good.

251
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:35,120
(Who just entered my room?)

252
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,879
(The pool is my paradise and my hell)

253
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:13,279
(The pool is my paradise)

254
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:15,399
(and my hell.)

255
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,399
What does this mean?

256
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,720
You're done with work?

257
00:13:49,039 --> 00:13:50,360
(This pool...)

258
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,679
(What's the secret?)

259
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:06,159
You finally remembered me.

260
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:16,220
(Smug)

261
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:25,740
(So mad she messed up her words)

262
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:35,260
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

263
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:40,100
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

264
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:44,660
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

265
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:49,580
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

266
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:53,380
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

267
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:58,180
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

268
00:14:58,180 --> 00:15:01,020
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

269
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:03,700
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

270
00:15:04,060 --> 00:15:09,620
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

271
00:15:10,020 --> 00:15:16,820
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

272
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:21,780
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

273
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:28,740
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

274
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:35,860
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

275
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:40,540
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

276
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:43,900
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

277
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:50,820
♪Right as I confess my love♪
